{"tid":827645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(憤怒的葡萄) 《紐時》刊游蕙禎文章　湯家驊不滿","createTime":"2018-09-19T05:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T05:52:15.000Z","uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5473aabb66e11396428d13d90c356a4d7e3c2223","tid":827645,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E5%88%8A%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF-%E6%88%91%E5%92%8C%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8A%95%E7%A8%BF%E5%9D%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B4%2590%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%2588%258A%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%2595%2599%25E7%25A6%258E%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A8%25BF%25E5%259D%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592&d=5RgmMYkHYhMYhPq%2FaWXbs%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=d2e84c74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B4%2590%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%2588%258A%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%2595%2599%25E7%25A6%258E%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A8%25BF%25E5%259D%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592&h=eb358bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E5%88%8A%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF-%E6%88%91%E5%92%8C%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8A%95%E7%A8%BF%E5%9D%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92</a>/<br />\n《紐約時報》周日刊登青年新政游蕙禎文章，內容提及香港脫離北京獨立是唯一出路。行政會議成員湯家驊今早於社交媒體批評《紐時》，提到早前自己和前律政司司長袁國強曾多次就法治問題撰文，該報全數拒登，「但對港獨、破壞香港法治的文章卻一律照單全收」，「令人感到遺憾和憤怒」。<br />\n湯家驊今早在 facebook 貼出《頭條日報》一篇報道，內容關於青年新游蕙禎在《紐約時報》撰文，及全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳的回應。湯家驊稱，《紐約時報》是一份「頗為奇怪的報紙」，指早前他和前律政司司長袁國強均曾多次就香港法治、憲法及法庭判決問題撰文，但對方卻全數拒絕刊登，甚至連以讀者來函方式也拒絕。<br />\n他又批評，《紐時》在拒絕他及袁國強投稿的同時，又「對港獨、破壞香港法治的文章一律照單全收」，使香港在國際「不斷被偏頗言論抹黑，卻毫無自辯機會」，令人感到遺憾和憤怒。<br />\n青年新政游蕙禎日前於《紐約時報》撰文，以《Democracy's Demise in Hong Kong》（香港民主的衰亡）為題，指自1997年香港主權移交後，香港的民主已被中國侵蝕至幾近完全被破壞，認為香港脫離北京獨立是唯一出路。她在文中說：「香港唯一的出路是脫離北京，成立新的民主國度。」"},{"pid":"18e635b112dd56918de59913d279f9fcfba5714a","tid":827645,"uid":108347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"對攪完細路可以消遙法外的人我都好撚不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b570d9592c47b412d8a3097859aa7ef321a6b6","tid":827645,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"憤怒的湯渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又奶777, 又奶港共, 又奶中共, 又想博外國勢力眼球<br />\n點個個個當佢透明: 行能開啦, _ _ _ _ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69186d47a00a321ef61366e36c1546c3659060ef","tid":827645,"uid":203045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"有冇nyt link"},{"pid":"c70d4687463d880d1f89735597d57302569dfb87","tid":827645,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>淚</strong></span></span>"}]}